  "markup": "\u003Cp style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;\u0022 class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EPurpose:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E To provide a structured process for addressing performance issues and policy violations, ensuring clear expectations, opportunities for improvement, consistent accountability, and fairness, while encouraging continuous improvement.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;\u0022 class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EProcedure:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Col start=\u00221\u0022 type=\u00221\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cli class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022 style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1; tab-stops: list 1.0in;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EGeneral Principles:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E Discipline will be applied fairly and consistently, focusing on correcting behavior. All actions will be documented. Employees will generally have an opportunity to respond.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022 style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1; tab-stops: list 1.0in;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDisciplinary Steps (typical, may vary)\u003C/strong\u003E:\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022 style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level3 lfo1; tab-stops: list 1.5in;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EVerbal Warning:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E For minor infractions/first-time issues; manager discusses, clarifies expectations, documents discussion.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022 style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level3 lfo1; tab-stops: list 1.5in;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EWritten Warning:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E For repeated minor infractions, failure to improve, or more serious initial violations; written document outlining issue, expectations, consequences, and timeframe. Employee signs to acknowledge receipt.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022 style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level3 lfo1; tab-stops: list 1.5in;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EFinal Written Warning / Suspension\u003C/strong\u003E:\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E For continued failure to improve, repeat serious offenses, or significant single violations; emphasizes seriousness, often includes unpaid suspension (1-5 days). States further violations will result in termination.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022 style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level3 lfo1; tab-stops: list 1.5in;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ETermination of Employment\u003C/strong\u003E:\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E For continued failure to meet standards after previous actions, or for severe misconduct warranting immediate separation.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cli class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022 style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1; tab-stops: list 1.0in;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ECircumstances for Skipping Steps\u003C/strong\u003E:\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E Neumo reserves the right to apply more severe action, including immediate suspension or termination, for serious misconduct (e.g., theft, violence, gross insubordination, breach of confidentiality, serious safety violations, drug/alcohol policy violations, harassment/discrimination etc.).\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022 style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1; tab-stops: list 1.0in;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EEmployee Right to Discuss\u003C/strong\u003E:\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E Employees receiving disciplinary action may discuss it with their manager or the People \u0026amp; Culture Team Business Partner if they believe it is unfair or inaccurate.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022 style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1; tab-stops: list 1.0in;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENo Employment Contract:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003E This policy does not create an employment contract or alter the \u0022at-will\u0022 nature of employment.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E"
}]]></Value>
