  "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EWe utilize a progressive discipline process to address performance issues and policy violations, providing you with clear expectations, opportunities for improvement, and consistent accountability. This approach aims to correct behavior and performance deficiencies through a series of steps, which may include verbal warnings, written warnings, suspension, and ultimately, termination of employment if issues persist or are severe. The specific steps taken will depend on the nature and severity of the issue.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
